      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646763/RenderMan_KaBoomBox_title.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433158447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646763/RenderMan_KaBoomBox_title.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433158447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646791\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_KaBoomBox_title.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646763\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"f915e90b-c93a-45c3-8dfe-f6c698c2056d\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/>Welcome to the RenderMan Kaboom Box HDA </p><p>The HDA will greatly speedup up your pyro and volume workflow, allowing artists to quickly and easily lookdev and render explosions, fire, candles, and anything else in between.  The HDA offers both basic and advanced pyro lookdev controls plus a few presets to get you going quickly and easily.  </p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://assets.renderman.pixar.com/resources/kaboom-box/kaboom_box.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download</a></p><p><br/><br/>At the heart of the HDA is a complex and robust PxrVolume shading network, developed especially for RenderMan by <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/hopeschroers/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hope Schroers</a>, one of the many very talented VFX TD's at Pixar Animation Studios.<br/><br/></p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646763/RenderMan_KaBoomBox_HoudiniIcon.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433158208&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646763/RenderMan_KaBoomBox_HoudiniIcon.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433158208&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646785\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_KaBoomBox_HoudiniIcon.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646763\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"f1a20a07-9cc0-49b6-a07f-2bac9b8ed90f\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/></p><p><div class=\"embeddedObject conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-macro-id=\"ed64982f-8e57-403a-a8d4-3410e95184d0\" data-macro-name=\"multimedia\">\n    <video src=\"/wiki/download/attachments/544646763/KaBoomBox_EXP_01.mp4\" height=\"540\" width=\"960\" autoplay=\"\" controls=\"\">\n        Your browser does not support the HTML5 video element\n</video>\n\n</div></p><p><br/></p>"
